title: 'Dancing With the Stars' Pro Cheryl Burke Is Dating Matthew Lawrence Again – See Their Cute Snaps!
text: 'Dancing With the Stars' Pro Cheryl Burke Is Dating Matthew Lawrence Again – See Their Cute Snaps! by Desiree Murphy 5:00 PM PST, February 16, 2017 Photo: Getty Images Cheryl Burke and Matthew Lawrence have reignited their romance! The Dancing With the Stars pro and the Melissa & Joey star are officially dating again, ET confirmed on Thursday. The two hinted they were back together via Snapchat earlier this month, when Burke shared pics from their trip to Big Sur, California. Photo: Snapchat The 32-year-old dancer even typed out her beau's Snapchat name, @mattlawrence, over a few of the photos. Photo: Snapchat A post shared by Cheryl Burke (@cherylburke) on Feb 7, 2017 at 3:57pm PST Lawrence, 37, first met Burke in 2006 when his brother, Joey Lawrence, was a contestant on Dancing With the Stars . They dated for about a year before calling it quits in 2008. WATCH: 'Dancing With the Stars' Pro Edyta Sliwinska Reveals She's Having a Girl! In more exciting DWTS news, pro dancer Edyta Sliwinska is expecting a baby girl! While chatting with ET at OK Magazine 's Pre-GRAMMY Party last week, Sliwinska opened up about how she and husband Alec Mazo are prepping for baby No. 2. Hear more in the video below.
